WEBVTT

00:21.184 --> 00:22.464
笙ｪThat day笙ｪ

00:22.880 --> 00:24.448
笙ｪNothing stays together forever笙ｪ

00:24.448 --> 00:25.792
笙ｪI've quit romance笙ｪ

00:26.218 --> 00:27.920
笙ｪWho hasn't failed again笙ｪ

00:27.920 --> 00:31.424
笙ｪCrying in death笙ｪ

00:31.424 --> 00:34.016
笙ｪAnd in life笙ｪ

00:34.432 --> 00:36.370
笙ｪEven now笙ｪ

00:36.672 --> 00:38.656
笙ｪWe keep learning笙ｪ

00:38.656 --> 00:39.680
笙ｪIt's no surprise笙ｪ

00:39.744 --> 00:42.144
笙ｪBeing happy is so hard笙ｪ

00:42.144 --> 00:43.968
笙ｪWeirdly, I became a role model笙ｪ

00:44.736 --> 00:46.688
笙ｪOn the day we met again, we said hi笙ｪ

00:46.688 --> 00:52.896
笙ｪIt was a reminder,
a test, and a complaint笙ｪ

00:52.896 --> 00:56.003
笙ｪWho can do anything without regret笙ｪ

00:56.003 --> 00:59.424
笙ｪI am all right笙ｪ

01:00.480 --> 01:05.074
笙ｪMay you live in peace笙ｪ

01:05.074 --> 01:07.456
笙ｪLet the world roar笙ｪ

01:07.456 --> 01:09.732
笙ｪSounds like a carnival笙ｪ

01:09.732 --> 01:14.453
笙ｪBeing alive is never dull笙ｪ

01:14.453 --> 01:18.830
笙ｪHow wonderful to be free笙ｪ

01:18.830 --> 01:23.485
笙ｪI became even better without you笙ｪ

01:23.485 --> 01:25.824
笙ｪNothing can be perfect笙ｪ

01:25.824 --> 01:28.224
笙ｪWe bless each other in pain笙ｪ

01:28.224 --> 01:34.234
笙ｪWe nod and smile笙ｪ

01:35.328 --> 01:36.288
笙ｪMay we both be well笙ｪ

01:36.288 --> 01:41.024
= Love's Ambition=

01:41.040 --> 01:43.984
=Episode 21=

01:54.138 --> 01:54.938
Actually,

01:56.177 --> 01:57.097
our last vacation

01:57.858 --> 01:58.858
was our honeymoon.

02:08.057 --> 02:09.538
I need to tell you something.

02:10.138 --> 02:11.698
Jiang Liang invested in Yan Studio.

02:12.057 --> 02:12.538
He...

02:12.578 --> 02:13.337
Jiang Liang?

02:15.177 --> 02:16.177
What does he know?

02:16.858 --> 02:18.138
He relies on his sister.

02:19.298 --> 02:20.657
He doesn't do anything.

02:20.657 --> 02:21.418
He's no good.

02:22.258 --> 02:23.937
He gave me some advice

02:24.657 --> 02:25.978
that was quite practical.

02:26.378 --> 02:27.777
He's not so clueless.

02:28.337 --> 02:29.098
When did he

02:29.418 --> 02:30.418
give you advice?

02:31.337 --> 02:32.057
A month ago.

02:32.457 --> 02:33.497
I ran into him

02:33.497 --> 02:34.177
at the cafe.

02:34.617 --> 02:35.497
A month ago?

02:36.138 --> 02:36.897
Why didn't you

02:36.937 --> 02:38.177
tell me you needed funds?

02:39.418 --> 02:40.457
Back then...

02:44.298 --> 02:45.457
Why would I tell you?

02:50.018 --> 02:50.617
Who am I

02:51.617 --> 02:52.418
to you?

02:55.897 --> 02:56.418
Yeah.

02:57.818 --> 02:58.937
I shouldn't interfere.

02:59.858 --> 03:01.177
I should thank you.

03:02.578 --> 03:03.538
You secured funding

03:04.378 --> 03:05.337
from an investor.

03:06.057 --> 03:07.418
That's why you're helping

03:07.897 --> 03:09.418
your soon-to-be ex-husband

03:10.217 --> 03:11.457
for some pocket money.

03:12.457 --> 03:13.897
How noble of you.

03:15.258 --> 03:16.057
Do you have to

03:16.057 --> 03:17.418
be so sarcastic?

03:22.698 --> 03:23.937
I don't want to argue.

03:24.258 --> 03:25.217
Let's be serious.

03:25.818 --> 03:27.057
Before I agreed

03:27.057 --> 03:28.177
to help you,

03:29.978 --> 03:30.858
I had been

03:30.858 --> 03:31.818
at my wits' end.

03:32.418 --> 03:32.978
Jiang Liang

03:32.978 --> 03:33.858
introduced me

03:34.538 --> 03:35.777
to a photographer.

03:35.978 --> 03:36.538
But he didn't

03:36.538 --> 03:37.578
promise to invest.

03:37.818 --> 03:39.737
My sister called me just now,
saying that

03:39.858 --> 03:40.457
Jiang Liang saw

03:40.457 --> 03:41.217
the latest video

03:41.217 --> 03:42.217
and decided to invest.

03:42.617 --> 03:44.018
I told you immediately.

03:44.657 --> 03:45.818
Isn't that prompt enough?

03:52.897 --> 03:53.617
True.

03:56.018 --> 03:58.298
I lied about having investors

03:58.858 --> 03:59.698
the other night.

04:08.978 --> 04:09.858
Ms. Xu.

04:10.057 --> 04:11.818
You're such an impressive actress.

04:12.418 --> 04:13.538
Who knows what other lies

04:13.538 --> 04:14.258
you've told?

04:24.578 --> 04:25.217
I've told

04:25.217 --> 04:26.097
a million lies.

04:28.378 --> 04:28.938
I had a fever

04:29.417 --> 04:30.618
when I interviewed you

04:30.857 --> 04:31.738
at Jinda Group.

04:31.857 --> 04:32.417
It was real.

04:32.938 --> 04:33.777
But I didn't faint.

04:39.097 --> 04:39.698
Mr. Shen.

04:40.018 --> 04:40.618
Sorry to have

04:40.777 --> 04:41.498
kept you waiting.

04:42.217 --> 04:43.258
Let's talk

04:43.337 --> 04:44.018
over lunch.

04:57.178 --> 04:58.977
The band-aid I gave you at the hospital

05:00.457 --> 05:01.897
was bought by Secretary Chen.

05:03.297 --> 05:05.337
I saw how moved you were,

05:05.738 --> 05:06.657
so I stayed silent.

05:11.258 --> 05:12.138
Also,

05:12.698 --> 05:14.097
when you applied for the job,

05:14.457 --> 05:15.217
I read your post

05:15.217 --> 05:16.857
during the interview. Remember?

05:17.618 --> 05:18.457
You wrote,

05:19.457 --> 05:21.018
"If Grandma has ever

05:21.018 --> 05:22.618
made osmanthus jam for you,

05:23.738 --> 05:26.537
you'll never feel lonely."

05:28.297 --> 05:29.578
Total nonsense.

05:30.097 --> 05:31.537
Melodramatic rambling.

05:43.417 --> 05:44.537
Didn't I tell you

05:44.578 --> 05:46.178
I learned ballet in school?

05:46.657 --> 05:47.657
I learned street dance.

05:47.977 --> 05:48.698
Popping.

05:48.897 --> 05:49.657
Breaking.

05:49.875 --> 05:51.178
Come on!

05:51.178 --> 05:52.258
Listen to me.

05:52.938 --> 05:54.217
Every outfit you chose for me

05:54.217 --> 05:55.777
disappointed me.

05:55.977 --> 05:57.378
The colors, quality,

05:57.537 --> 05:58.217
and taste

05:58.297 --> 05:59.297
were all terrible.

05:59.618 --> 06:01.138
Reflect on yourself.

06:01.258 --> 06:02.217
Look inward.

06:02.217 --> 06:03.138
Is it because

06:03.138 --> 06:04.657
you're outdated and stuffy

06:04.738 --> 06:06.058
with taste behind the times?

06:07.297 --> 06:08.258
Your slicked-back hair

06:08.457 --> 06:09.258
never changes.

06:10.058 --> 06:10.777
And your suit

06:11.457 --> 06:12.457
is always the same.

06:12.818 --> 06:13.337
What's wrong?

06:13.417 --> 06:14.417
Are you bed linens?

06:14.417 --> 06:15.337
And those glasses.

06:15.378 --> 06:16.178
Are you nearsighted?

06:16.297 --> 06:17.417
Why do you wear them?

06:17.417 --> 06:17.977
What for?

06:18.018 --> 06:19.138
To act like old money?

06:25.217 --> 06:26.178
I'm better than you.

06:27.018 --> 06:29.657
You claim to be a food expert

06:30.058 --> 06:31.297
and host Family Feast.

06:32.097 --> 06:33.537
None of the food

06:34.657 --> 06:36.738
you cook tastes good.

06:36.777 --> 06:37.738
It's awful.

06:37.818 --> 06:39.457
I force myself to eat it, okay?

06:39.537 --> 06:40.738
The jewelry pieces you gave me

06:41.698 --> 06:42.938
are tacky and tasteless.

06:43.698 --> 06:44.977
Not a single one I like.

06:46.288 --> 06:47.472
Forced myself to accept them.

06:49.018 --> 06:49.578
Fine.

06:50.178 --> 06:51.018
I'll tell

06:51.537 --> 06:52.698
Secretary Chen.

06:53.417 --> 06:54.698
I didn't buy them, anyway.

06:55.337 --> 06:56.657
I didn't even check them.

07:01.258 --> 07:02.138
Doesn't matter.

07:02.897 --> 07:04.337
It doesn't matter.

07:04.777 --> 07:05.818
Men's gifts are

07:05.818 --> 07:06.618
all the same.

07:06.738 --> 07:07.698
I'm used to it.

07:08.578 --> 07:09.258
Used to it?

07:10.498 --> 07:11.417
How many guys

07:11.897 --> 07:12.618
have you dated?

07:12.618 --> 07:13.616
How many did I tell you?

07:14.618 --> 07:15.777
You said I was the only one.

07:15.857 --> 07:16.297
Yeah.

07:16.618 --> 07:17.378
Just one.

07:17.698 --> 07:18.698
Plus a zero.

07:35.457 --> 07:36.496
Three days later, the 8th,

07:36.857 --> 07:38.378
meet me at the Bureau at 10 AM.

07:50.777 --> 07:52.857
Yuanhang is a major investment firm.

07:53.217 --> 07:54.457
We're just a start-up.

07:54.818 --> 07:56.618
Why would Jiang Liang invest in us?

07:56.698 --> 07:58.297
Investing in successful start-ups

07:58.297 --> 07:59.378
is just bandwagoning.

07:59.417 --> 08:00.618
Investing now shows

08:01.217 --> 08:02.178
vision.

08:02.337 --> 08:04.138
- Vision.
- Vision.

08:05.498 --> 08:05.938
Alright.

08:06.297 --> 08:07.618
We have an investor.

08:07.698 --> 08:08.977
Our video got 10k likes.

08:09.018 --> 08:09.698
We're doing well.

08:10.058 --> 08:11.698
Let's hope everything picks up.

08:11.777 --> 08:12.457
Fingers crossed.

08:12.857 --> 08:13.857
Only good news ahead.

08:14.258 --> 08:14.897
So

08:15.337 --> 08:16.657
let's drink till we drop.

08:17.977 --> 08:18.698
Till we drop.

08:18.777 --> 08:19.657
- Cheers.
- Cheers.

08:19.897 --> 08:21.258
- Cheers.
- Cheers.

08:37.378 --> 08:38.657
I heard your Chinese grades

08:38.657 --> 08:39.577
dropped recently.

08:40.098 --> 08:41.697
Do you need a tutor?

08:42.738 --> 08:44.697
No tutor beats sis-in-law.

08:45.858 --> 08:47.458
She's so patient

08:47.697 --> 08:49.577
and explains things clearly.

08:50.577 --> 08:52.297
I get it right away.

08:55.138 --> 08:55.618
Haoming,

08:55.697 --> 08:57.057
when are you bringing her back?

08:58.738 --> 08:59.937
She's still busy with work

09:00.697 --> 09:01.738
and won't return soon.

09:03.537 --> 09:05.458
You clearly miss her.

09:05.577 --> 09:06.697
Just beg for forgiveness.

09:06.697 --> 09:08.218
I don't miss her.

09:10.498 --> 09:11.897
Say one thing and mean another.

09:12.458 --> 09:13.738
That's the idiom for you.

09:15.258 --> 09:17.138
She's definitely still angry.

09:17.618 --> 09:18.577
Did you apologize

09:18.577 --> 09:19.817
sincerely to her?

09:21.777 --> 09:23.378
Seems you've mastered Chinese.

09:24.138 --> 09:25.738
Idioms flow naturally now.

09:27.937 --> 09:29.057
Wait a minute.

09:30.177 --> 09:30.657
Sit.

09:32.458 --> 09:33.417
Sit down.

09:39.218 --> 09:39.978
First,

09:40.057 --> 09:41.657
sis-in-law taught me that idiom.

09:42.057 --> 09:43.777
Second, you should know this.

09:44.378 --> 09:45.738
When guys get rejected,

09:45.738 --> 09:47.057
it's okay.

09:47.378 --> 09:49.057
Even if you're rejected 100 times,

09:49.098 --> 09:50.378
you must win her back

09:50.378 --> 09:50.978
in the end.

09:51.338 --> 09:51.978
Got it?

09:54.777 --> 09:55.618
If only

09:55.618 --> 09:56.657
you could study with

09:56.697 --> 09:57.577
such perseverance.

09:58.417 --> 09:59.697
Mind your own business.

09:59.937 --> 10:00.378
Okay?

10:00.577 --> 10:01.218
Okay.

10:01.817 --> 10:02.738
My performance is

10:02.738 --> 10:03.978
none of your business, either.

10:13.218 --> 10:14.618
Close the door on your way out.

10:26.138 --> 10:27.657
(When guys get rejected,)

10:27.657 --> 10:28.657
(it's okay.)

10:29.057 --> 10:30.738
Even if you're rejected 100 times,

10:31.218 --> 10:32.897
you must win her back

10:32.897 --> 10:33.458
in the end.

10:46.338 --> 10:47.537
What's up?

10:49.177 --> 10:50.297
Are you there?

10:53.297 --> 10:54.057
(Shen Haoming)
Going to bed?

11:00.794 --> 11:01.657
(Xu Yan)

11:01.657 --> 11:02.218
(Not yet.)

11:02.577 --> 11:03.138
(What's up?)

11:06.138 --> 11:07.858
(Shen Haoming)
(Mr. Baraikin and I)

11:07.858 --> 11:09.258
(spoke on the phone.)

11:09.537 --> 11:12.018
(He'll visit Jinda in a few days.)

11:15.577 --> 11:16.858
(If you're free,)

11:17.057 --> 11:18.657
(let's have dinner together.)

11:20.458 --> 11:21.138
(I can't.)

11:21.458 --> 11:22.378
(I've been swamped.)

11:22.657 --> 11:23.537
(Give him my regards.)

11:27.657 --> 11:28.177
(Shen Haoming)
(Alright.)

11:29.258 --> 11:30.577
(I'll have Chen)

11:30.618 --> 11:32.018
(wire you the money.)

11:36.978 --> 11:37.458
(Xu Yan)
(Thanks.)

11:41.537 --> 11:42.537
How do I win her back?

11:43.098 --> 11:44.378
Should I keep arguing with her?

11:44.657 --> 11:45.858
I'm such an idiot.

11:58.657 --> 11:59.098
Again.

11:59.498 --> 12:01.218
You're the sparring partner applicant?

12:05.897 --> 12:06.897
With your physique,

12:06.978 --> 12:07.858
can you handle it?

12:08.297 --> 12:09.057
No problem.

12:09.417 --> 12:10.657
In our line of work,

12:11.297 --> 12:12.498
we must endure hits.

12:13.138 --> 12:13.897
Not everyone

12:13.897 --> 12:14.817
can withstand this.

12:15.537 --> 12:16.018
Sir.

12:16.338 --> 12:18.098
I want to learn how to take hits.

12:18.618 --> 12:19.098
Fine.

12:19.697 --> 12:20.618
Let's give it a try.

12:21.297 --> 12:22.738
When do we start?

12:25.297 --> 12:25.937
Right now.

12:26.297 --> 12:27.138
Headshot first.

12:27.817 --> 12:28.618
Pardon?

12:29.850 --> 12:32.048
(Treatise on Superfluous Things)

12:32.048 --> 12:33.178
While...

12:40.138 --> 12:40.738
Grandma, look.

12:41.177 --> 12:41.657
See?

12:41.697 --> 12:43.218
Nice office, right?

12:43.777 --> 12:44.858
Let me show you around.

12:45.018 --> 12:45.498
See?

12:46.297 --> 12:47.018
This is

12:47.177 --> 12:48.817
our main lobby.

12:49.018 --> 12:50.018
- The second floor.
- So spacious.

12:51.057 --> 12:52.297
Display wall.

12:52.378 --> 12:53.098
See?

12:53.417 --> 12:54.258
And we have...

12:54.537 --> 12:55.297
Look who this is.

12:55.297 --> 12:56.218
Grandma.

12:56.618 --> 12:57.098
Look.

12:57.218 --> 12:58.096
You like our office?

12:59.618 --> 13:01.098
Yan, Lin,

13:01.577 --> 13:02.378
you girls really

13:02.498 --> 13:04.138
picked a great place.

13:04.297 --> 13:05.858
Spacious and bright.

13:06.098 --> 13:06.978
I'm here.

13:07.338 --> 13:08.018
Is it Grandma?

13:09.297 --> 13:09.897
Hi, Grandma.

13:09.978 --> 13:10.458
Grandma.

13:10.498 --> 13:12.378
This is our designer

13:12.537 --> 13:14.138
I keep telling you about.

13:14.138 --> 13:14.897
Yao.

13:15.057 --> 13:16.897
Here's our long-legged model,

13:16.897 --> 13:17.657
Guan.

13:17.657 --> 13:18.177
Look.

13:18.417 --> 13:19.577
- Hi Grandma.
- See her legs?

13:21.458 --> 13:22.738
Yan, Lin,

13:23.057 --> 13:25.177
and your partners,

13:26.218 --> 13:28.098
Yao, Guan, right?

13:28.338 --> 13:28.858
You girls

13:29.018 --> 13:29.897
are very talented

13:29.897 --> 13:31.417
young ladies.

13:32.978 --> 13:34.338
I'm so happy

13:34.378 --> 13:35.858
to see you working together.

13:36.657 --> 13:38.618
I wish you a grand opening

13:39.216 --> 13:40.098
and booming business.

13:40.138 --> 13:42.098
- Thanks, Grandma.
- Thanks, Grandma.

13:42.098 --> 13:43.458
Grandma's the best.

13:43.978 --> 13:44.498
Alright then.

13:44.537 --> 13:46.018
I won't keep you any longer.

13:46.177 --> 13:47.057
You're busy girls.

13:47.777 --> 13:48.297
Okay.

13:48.338 --> 13:49.018
Bye, Grandma.

13:49.057 --> 13:49.937
- Bye-bye.
- Bye-bye.

13:49.978 --> 13:50.537
I have to go.

13:51.138 --> 13:51.897
Go ahead.

13:52.297 --> 13:53.098
Bye, Grandma.

13:53.498 --> 13:54.057
Miss you.

13:56.937 --> 13:58.258
Why are you hanging up?

13:58.258 --> 13:59.177
Talk to me more.

14:00.297 --> 14:02.738
I just want to tell you.

14:03.937 --> 14:04.577
Life is not

14:05.338 --> 14:07.177
all about making money.

14:08.378 --> 14:10.697
You need inherent confidence.

14:11.177 --> 14:12.738
I hope you can

14:12.858 --> 14:14.417
maintain good spirits

14:15.018 --> 14:18.378
while working hard.

14:18.937 --> 14:19.738
Okay, Grandma.

14:20.817 --> 14:21.258
Yan.

14:21.258 --> 14:22.177
Remember that...

14:22.338 --> 14:22.858
Yan.

14:22.858 --> 14:23.897
Take your medicine.

14:23.978 --> 14:24.777
Ms. Xu.

14:24.777 --> 14:25.458
I have to go.

14:26.458 --> 14:26.897
What's up?

14:26.897 --> 14:28.297
This is my office?

14:28.897 --> 14:29.417
Yeah.

14:29.858 --> 14:30.858
Yan.

14:31.258 --> 14:33.138
My design studio is so spacious.

14:33.138 --> 14:33.817
Is it enough?

14:34.018 --> 14:36.138
More than enough.

14:37.378 --> 14:37.937
Alright.

14:38.937 --> 14:39.417
Alright.

14:39.978 --> 14:40.738
From now on,

14:40.858 --> 14:42.218
this will be our starting point.

14:42.378 --> 14:43.218
Let's go big.

14:43.338 --> 14:44.138
Let's go big.

14:44.297 --> 14:45.098
Let's tidy up.

14:45.098 --> 14:45.618
Okay.

14:45.840 --> 14:47.676
笙ｪSharp tailoring笙ｪ

14:48.458 --> 14:49.098
This is mine.

14:49.177 --> 14:49.897
Take it away.

14:50.218 --> 14:50.858
It's my spot.

14:50.858 --> 14:51.777
To my office. Thanks.

14:51.777 --> 14:52.177
Got it.

14:52.537 --> 14:53.177
Keep going.

14:53.378 --> 14:54.417
Here's your keyboard.

14:54.537 --> 14:54.978
Come on.

14:55.344 --> 14:57.338
笙ｪLike a raw diamond笙ｪ

14:57.338 --> 14:58.138
It's my spot.

14:58.138 --> 14:58.897
It's bright.

14:59.098 --> 14:59.417
Okay.

14:59.458 --> 15:00.537
So this is my spot.

15:00.944 --> 15:02.864
笙ｪEvery frame's perfection笙ｪ

15:02.864 --> 15:04.880
笙ｪMy beauty's defined by none笙ｪ

15:06.177 --> 15:06.897
What's this?

15:07.258 --> 15:07.978
A computer.

15:08.138 --> 15:08.937
For work.

15:09.018 --> 15:11.577
- Can I have it in dressing room?
- How much is this?

15:12.738 --> 15:14.297
Bring two more boxes.

15:14.777 --> 15:15.937
- The ones with materials.
- Right here.

15:15.937 --> 15:16.897
Help me out.

15:16.897 --> 15:17.858
- Help me.
- On the table.

15:19.057 --> 15:19.417
Thanks.

15:19.657 --> 15:20.537
Let's unpack this.

15:20.577 --> 15:21.057
Slowly.

15:21.057 --> 15:21.777
Careful.

15:37.258 --> 15:37.978
Mr. Shen.

15:38.657 --> 15:39.577
The design has been

15:39.618 --> 15:40.177
revised.

15:40.697 --> 15:42.338
The design team wants to meet.

15:42.897 --> 15:44.138
I checked your schedule.

15:44.498 --> 15:44.978
You're

15:44.978 --> 15:45.978
only available on the 8th

15:47.817 --> 15:48.458
this month.

15:50.697 --> 15:52.458
The Legal Department added three clauses

15:53.018 --> 15:54.018
to the contract annex

15:54.018 --> 15:54.897
as requested.

15:55.498 --> 15:56.018
Also,

15:56.138 --> 15:57.978
they modified clauses

15:57.978 --> 15:58.777
No. 3 and No. 8.

15:59.297 --> 15:59.897
I've booked

16:00.297 --> 16:01.738
private room No. 8 in Yipinxuan

16:02.057 --> 16:02.738
for tonight.

16:07.098 --> 16:07.897
Mr. Shen.

16:08.777 --> 16:09.777
Is something wrong?

16:11.458 --> 16:12.138
From now on,

16:13.258 --> 16:15.098
I don't want to hear the number "eight".

16:28.338 --> 16:28.897
Mr. Shen.

16:29.138 --> 16:30.417
Land acquisition evaluation

16:30.458 --> 16:31.338
and market research

16:31.378 --> 16:32.417
on Project 018

16:32.417 --> 16:33.258
have been completed.

16:33.537 --> 16:34.978
Most land acquisitions

16:34.978 --> 16:35.978
are feasible.

16:36.378 --> 16:38.378
Except that

16:38.417 --> 16:39.297
a 120-mu plot

16:39.297 --> 16:40.577
in the core zone

16:40.817 --> 16:42.258
has been purchased.

16:42.897 --> 16:44.338
It was acquired

16:44.577 --> 16:45.498
ten years ago.

16:47.537 --> 16:48.338
Ten years ago?

16:48.738 --> 16:50.338
It was a remote wasteland back then

16:50.978 --> 16:51.978
without any

16:52.258 --> 16:53.057
development plans.

16:54.618 --> 16:55.738
Who'd buy land there?

16:56.138 --> 16:57.897
Mr. Shen Haoming.

17:02.177 --> 17:02.577
Dad.

17:03.498 --> 17:04.337
You want to see me?

17:05.258 --> 17:07.018
You bought the 120-mu land

17:07.097 --> 17:08.337
of Project 018 a decade ago?

17:08.738 --> 17:09.418
Why?

17:12.297 --> 17:13.218
The government

17:14.018 --> 17:15.938
wanted to establish
a new free trade zone.

17:16.857 --> 17:17.577
The group

17:18.057 --> 17:19.337
conducted evaluations

17:19.898 --> 17:21.617
and prioritized development

17:21.658 --> 17:23.978
in the eastern and southern areas.

17:24.658 --> 17:25.178
First,

17:25.938 --> 17:27.218
they wanted to be close

17:27.777 --> 17:28.458
to downtown.

17:29.218 --> 17:29.817
Second,

17:30.337 --> 17:32.218
the eastern and southern peripherals

17:32.337 --> 17:34.537
had a relatively complete infrastructure

17:34.658 --> 17:35.458
for residential use.

17:35.817 --> 17:37.178
Everyone thought

17:37.857 --> 17:39.978
the northern area was barren land

17:40.418 --> 17:41.857
with no development value.

17:42.178 --> 17:42.698
Indeed.

17:42.817 --> 17:44.498
That's what the executives thought.

17:46.258 --> 17:46.857
But

17:47.577 --> 17:48.097
people

17:48.097 --> 17:49.698
overlooked one critical factor.

17:51.577 --> 17:52.297
High-speed rail.

17:55.297 --> 17:56.617
The rail network plan

17:57.377 --> 17:58.418
announced that year

17:59.258 --> 18:00.938
showed that the high-speed rail

18:01.498 --> 18:03.617
would connect major economic zones

18:04.297 --> 18:05.738
and reduce intercity distances.

18:06.698 --> 18:08.418
I studied the published blueprint.

18:09.258 --> 18:10.738
The rail extended to the north,

18:11.577 --> 18:13.377
intersecting with our free trade zone's

18:13.898 --> 18:15.337
intercity light rail system.

18:16.337 --> 18:18.498
A city's subway planning

18:18.898 --> 18:20.097
must coordinate with

18:20.137 --> 18:21.337
major transportation hubs.

18:22.178 --> 18:22.898
So, I predicted

18:23.537 --> 18:25.137
that the municipal government would

18:25.137 --> 18:26.617
leverage the transportation hub

18:27.057 --> 18:29.258
and establish a New District.

18:30.097 --> 18:31.258
So, I believed this land

18:31.337 --> 18:32.418
was worth investing in.

18:33.377 --> 18:34.258
That means

18:35.218 --> 18:37.018
you demonstrated remarkable foresight

18:37.297 --> 18:38.258
back then.

18:39.698 --> 18:40.978
I must thank you

18:41.018 --> 18:42.377
for sending me to the top schools

18:43.458 --> 18:44.537
where I learned

18:44.698 --> 18:46.137
diverse urban designs

18:46.258 --> 18:46.978
and planning.

18:48.218 --> 18:49.178
But I have a question.

18:50.537 --> 18:51.498
You wanted to

18:51.537 --> 18:52.617
acquire the project.

18:53.057 --> 18:53.938
You'd need money.

18:54.178 --> 18:55.577
Where did your funding come from?

18:57.057 --> 18:58.577
From my college classmates.

19:00.137 --> 19:01.297
They had

19:01.698 --> 19:02.777
considerable idle funds

19:03.337 --> 19:04.617
but lacked knowledge

19:04.738 --> 19:06.658
of profitable investment channels.

19:07.698 --> 19:08.857
I managed

19:09.097 --> 19:10.337
some short-term futures

19:10.498 --> 19:11.817
through the years,

19:12.018 --> 19:13.297
earning them good returns

19:13.617 --> 19:15.297
as well as their trust.

19:15.857 --> 19:16.537
I see.

19:18.577 --> 19:19.658
One more question.

19:21.137 --> 19:21.857
Since you've been

19:22.018 --> 19:24.218
operating this project for so long.

19:24.337 --> 19:25.698
What would you ask for

19:26.498 --> 19:27.418
to hand it over

19:27.537 --> 19:28.458
to our company?

19:28.577 --> 19:29.137
Feel free

19:29.337 --> 19:30.297
to make any requests.

19:30.577 --> 19:31.097
Alright?

19:34.738 --> 19:36.018
I'll transfer this land

19:36.978 --> 19:37.777
to the group

19:38.577 --> 19:40.258
to meet all corporate needs

19:40.738 --> 19:42.137
without any conditions.

19:46.418 --> 19:46.938
Why?

19:49.537 --> 19:49.978
Dad.

19:51.938 --> 19:53.817
I've been thinking about

19:55.577 --> 19:57.018
what happened with Haochen.

19:58.337 --> 19:59.498
It seems I've never

19:59.658 --> 20:00.537
properly apologized

20:00.698 --> 20:01.537
to you or Mom

20:02.097 --> 20:03.178
about this.

20:09.137 --> 20:10.418
Regarding this matter,

20:12.377 --> 20:13.178
your mom and I

20:13.178 --> 20:14.218
don't need apologies.

20:15.377 --> 20:16.777
We just want you to understand

20:18.097 --> 20:19.057
that everyone

20:19.057 --> 20:19.898
must take

20:20.297 --> 20:21.938
full responsibility for their actions.

20:23.577 --> 20:24.178
I understand.

20:25.938 --> 20:27.258
That's also my philosophy.

20:29.137 --> 20:30.018
But I've always

20:30.218 --> 20:31.297
hoped that you could

20:31.377 --> 20:32.297
understand me.

20:33.258 --> 20:35.258
But I never considered your feelings.

20:36.097 --> 20:37.898
I don't regret
what happened with Haochen.

20:39.418 --> 20:40.498
But I know it has

20:40.537 --> 20:41.777
caused you and Mom

20:41.777 --> 20:42.698
tremendous stress.

20:43.738 --> 20:44.817
This is my fault.

20:46.218 --> 20:47.938
I had a bad temper before.

20:48.498 --> 20:49.617
I acted tough

20:51.258 --> 20:52.857
because I was insecure

20:53.418 --> 20:54.097
and anxious.

20:54.738 --> 20:56.698
I didn't know what would happen.

20:59.978 --> 21:01.617
Eventually, I saw that you and Mom

21:02.777 --> 21:04.057
accepted Haochen,

21:05.777 --> 21:07.178
giving him a carefree

21:07.577 --> 21:08.617
living environment.

21:10.297 --> 21:11.617
Your tolerance

21:11.898 --> 21:13.537
truly empowered me.

21:18.777 --> 21:19.698
We've quarreled

21:21.938 --> 21:22.777
and fought

21:24.137 --> 21:24.898
quite enough.

21:27.777 --> 21:29.097
After I calmed down,

21:31.777 --> 21:32.777
I did realize

21:32.817 --> 21:33.857
why you doubted me

21:34.258 --> 21:35.057
both then

21:36.418 --> 21:37.817
and right now.

21:39.938 --> 21:40.817
I must

21:41.817 --> 21:43.057
take the responsibility.

21:45.577 --> 21:46.418
That's why

21:46.577 --> 21:47.537
I never intended

21:47.617 --> 21:48.857
to negotiate terms with you.

21:51.978 --> 21:53.018
You came back

21:54.577 --> 21:55.537
from the resort

21:55.577 --> 21:56.777
as a different person.

21:59.817 --> 22:01.218
(If you love someone,)

22:02.377 --> 22:03.498
you should trust them

22:04.218 --> 22:05.337
and believe their actions

22:05.337 --> 22:06.377
are meant to protect you.

22:07.018 --> 22:08.698
No matter how old we grow,

22:10.218 --> 22:11.337
in our elders' eyes,

22:11.537 --> 22:12.938
we'll always remain children.

22:13.777 --> 22:15.857
But their distrust doesn't equate

22:16.458 --> 22:18.377
to indifference or neglect.

22:21.658 --> 22:23.297
I'll send the land transfer agreement

22:23.738 --> 22:24.617
to the group.

22:28.018 --> 22:29.057
Listen, Haoming.

22:29.698 --> 22:30.698
If you can

22:30.938 --> 22:32.018
facilitate

22:32.137 --> 22:33.817
official collaboration with Baraikin

22:33.938 --> 22:34.938
and expand

22:34.938 --> 22:36.097
our overseas market,

22:36.377 --> 22:37.698
then I promise that

22:38.577 --> 22:40.178
I'll bring you onto the board.

22:41.658 --> 22:42.817
But remember this.

22:44.018 --> 22:45.337
Once you're in this game,

22:45.898 --> 22:47.297
you'll face doubts

22:47.377 --> 22:48.258
and even scrutiny

22:48.418 --> 22:49.297
from more people.

22:49.738 --> 22:50.617
Besides, I won't

22:50.978 --> 22:52.978
allow you to make any mistakes.

22:54.898 --> 22:55.377
Dad.

22:56.537 --> 22:57.297
I don't mind that.

22:58.297 --> 22:59.898
I just hope you can

23:00.617 --> 23:01.537
start trusting me.

23:02.658 --> 23:03.418
I also hope

23:04.218 --> 23:05.817
I can start trusting you.

23:07.617 --> 23:08.297
Come on, son.

23:08.817 --> 23:09.817
Walk with me.

23:17.018 --> 23:18.608
(Yan Studio)

23:24.898 --> 23:25.297
Sit.

23:25.898 --> 23:26.377
Hello.

23:26.458 --> 23:27.817
My name is Meng Zhao.

23:27.898 --> 23:29.738
I graduated from
Jingzhou Business University.

23:30.137 --> 23:31.097
I'm Zhao Kehuan

23:31.097 --> 23:32.738
from Jingzhou Communication University,

23:32.738 --> 23:33.898
majoring in Broadcasting.

23:34.018 --> 23:34.898
I'm Qu Xiaowan,

23:35.057 --> 23:36.178
24 years old.

23:36.337 --> 23:38.057
I worked at a 4A agency.

23:38.137 --> 23:39.258
I was a planner

23:39.258 --> 23:40.337
of Family Feast.

23:40.817 --> 23:42.178
What are you applying for?

23:42.498 --> 23:43.898
Promotion Specialist.

23:44.057 --> 23:44.912
Business Specialist.

23:45.018 --> 23:45.777
Anything will do.

23:45.857 --> 23:47.458
I'll do whatever you assign me.

23:47.617 --> 23:48.137
Rest assured.

23:48.218 --> 23:49.498
I'm highly action-oriented.

23:49.617 --> 23:50.377
I will complete

23:50.458 --> 23:51.498
any tasks given to me.

23:51.698 --> 23:52.498
She's like you.

23:53.057 --> 23:53.938
I'm not so direct.

23:54.817 --> 23:55.978
What's your expected salary?

23:56.178 --> 23:58.137
Depends on the workload.

23:58.498 --> 23:59.577
At my previous company,

23:59.698 --> 24:01.218
my salary was higher because

24:01.377 --> 24:02.337
I did a triple workload.

24:02.577 --> 24:03.857
I'll accept a normal salary

24:04.137 --> 24:05.018
for a normal workload.

24:05.178 --> 24:05.857
Don't worry.

24:06.458 --> 24:08.057
We'll hire more business specialists

24:08.337 --> 24:09.057
if needed.

24:09.498 --> 24:10.258
It would be great

24:10.337 --> 24:12.857
if the salary could be
a bit higher than my previous job.

24:13.258 --> 24:14.297
Otherwise, I can accept

24:14.297 --> 24:15.178
the same salary.

24:15.337 --> 24:16.218
I'm still young.

24:16.337 --> 24:18.218
Money isn't that important to me.

24:18.377 --> 24:19.418
Opportunity matters more.

24:20.137 --> 24:20.698
Thank you.

24:21.418 --> 24:21.898
Thank you.

24:23.386 --> 24:26.418
(Yan Studio)

24:26.418 --> 24:27.658
Welcome to Yan Studio.

24:29.057 --> 24:30.097
Thanks for joining us.

24:30.418 --> 24:30.938
Yan.

24:31.097 --> 24:32.178
I'll go wherever you are.

24:32.617 --> 24:33.218
I promise

24:33.258 --> 24:34.097
I'll work hard.

24:34.097 --> 24:36.336
(Yan Studio)

24:46.297 --> 24:47.337
Mr. Jiang Liang.

24:47.537 --> 24:48.617
Welcome to Yan Studio.

24:49.178 --> 24:49.658
Do you like

24:49.817 --> 24:50.777
the environment here?

24:51.097 --> 24:51.738
It's amazing.

24:53.218 --> 24:53.857
Your first video

24:53.857 --> 24:54.777
has done so well.

24:54.857 --> 24:56.218
When will you post the second one?

24:57.137 --> 24:58.018
(Yan Studio)
Let's get in.

24:58.218 --> 24:59.018
The staff are ready

24:59.018 --> 24:59.738
to brief you.

24:59.938 --> 25:00.817
- Alright.
- This way.

25:55.290 --> 25:57.776
(Civil Affairs Bureau, 8th)

26:13.498 --> 26:15.056
(Shen Haoming)

26:26.738 --> 26:27.137
Hello.

26:28.337 --> 26:28.817
Hello.

26:29.698 --> 26:30.258
What's wrong?

26:31.738 --> 26:33.178
Nothing. Just a reminder.

26:35.218 --> 26:36.337
Tomorrow's the 8th.

26:38.137 --> 26:39.297
See you at the Bureau

26:39.377 --> 26:40.018
at 10 AM.

26:41.137 --> 26:41.938
Bad timing.

26:42.498 --> 26:44.137
I'm on a business trip in Russia.

26:45.297 --> 26:46.537
You went to Russia?

26:47.617 --> 26:48.297
You know,

26:48.337 --> 26:50.097
things are going well with Mr. Baraikin.

26:50.617 --> 26:51.458
So I have to strike

26:51.898 --> 26:53.258
when the iron's hot.

26:56.577 --> 26:58.018
But didn't we agree to meet

26:59.178 --> 27:00.537
at the Bureau on the 8th?

27:02.418 --> 27:03.498
Next month, maybe.

27:04.218 --> 27:06.018
Then the application will expire.

27:08.178 --> 27:08.817
What can I do?

27:09.337 --> 27:10.018
I'm busy.

27:11.777 --> 27:13.218
I'm traveling to France,

27:13.297 --> 27:13.938
England,

27:14.057 --> 27:14.978
and so on.

27:15.738 --> 27:16.577
I can't go back.

27:17.898 --> 27:18.777
Shen Haoming.

27:18.938 --> 27:19.617
Do you have to

27:19.617 --> 27:20.738
go on a business trip now?

27:21.377 --> 27:23.377
Mr. Baraikin approached me.

27:23.698 --> 27:24.777
I can't tell him,

27:24.817 --> 27:26.018
"Let me get divorced first",

27:26.097 --> 27:26.537
can I?

27:27.018 --> 27:27.817
Come here.

27:28.218 --> 27:29.178
Mr. Baraikin needs me.

27:29.258 --> 27:29.898
I have to go.

27:29.938 --> 27:30.537
Coming.

27:30.777 --> 27:31.577
Okay, bye.

27:52.938 --> 27:54.018
Xin, stop running.

27:54.258 --> 27:55.137
You can't go in.

27:55.297 --> 27:56.218
You can't go in there.

27:56.258 --> 27:56.658
Be good.

28:03.258 --> 28:05.218
It's not a good angle.

28:11.178 --> 28:12.458
She'll believe it, right?

28:14.898 --> 28:15.817
I need more photos.

28:23.098 --> 28:25.712
(Yan)

28:47.377 --> 28:48.458
Next stop: Africa.

28:53.617 --> 28:54.658
Alexandria.

29:10.938 --> 29:11.498
Chen Lin.

29:12.418 --> 29:14.218
Photoshop these trees out.

29:15.738 --> 29:17.906
(A few days later)

29:31.698 --> 29:32.738
Hello? Yan.

29:34.218 --> 29:35.418
Is Shen Haoming in Jingzhou?

29:37.178 --> 29:38.297
Mr. Shen is in Moscow.

29:42.738 --> 29:44.178
Got it. Thanks.

29:46.682 --> 29:49.200
(July 8th)

29:51.137 --> 29:51.658
Chen Lin.

29:51.898 --> 29:52.617
Did Xu Yan

29:52.817 --> 29:53.738
call you today?

29:53.898 --> 29:55.097
Just as you predicted.

29:55.458 --> 29:56.537
She called several times.

29:56.738 --> 29:57.218
Good.

29:57.938 --> 29:58.258
Okay.

29:58.377 --> 29:59.738
I won't be at the office.

29:59.898 --> 30:01.258
Call me if anything comes up.

30:24.418 --> 30:25.377
It's an illusion.

30:26.698 --> 30:27.498
It must be.

30:38.898 --> 30:39.498
Illusion.

30:51.297 --> 30:52.577
Aren't you in Russia?

30:54.698 --> 30:56.777
Which city is Shen Haoming in now?

30:57.938 --> 30:59.137
He's in Moscow.

31:00.377 --> 31:01.577
But he told me

31:01.577 --> 31:02.817
he's in Alexandria.

31:04.577 --> 31:05.698
Yeah, he's in Alexandria.

31:06.097 --> 31:06.978
My mistake, Yan.

31:07.377 --> 31:08.978
Mr. Shen is in Alexandria.

31:12.097 --> 31:13.938
But you just said he was in Russia.

31:15.178 --> 31:15.738
Yeah.

31:15.817 --> 31:17.218
Alexandria in Russia.

31:17.938 --> 31:19.658
Alexandria is in Egypt.

31:21.338 --> 31:22.032
(Paid Promotion)

31:25.698 --> 31:27.458
Doesn't Russia have a city
named Alexandria?

31:31.057 --> 31:32.738
I changed my schedule last minute.

31:34.978 --> 31:36.178
Thanks for cooperating.

31:38.537 --> 31:39.297
The Bureau, now.

31:39.898 --> 31:41.218
I changed my plans

31:41.218 --> 31:42.337
due to health issues.

31:42.337 --> 31:43.418
I'm seeing a doctor.

31:43.537 --> 31:44.137
What's wrong?

31:50.738 --> 31:51.418
Heart problems.

31:52.698 --> 31:53.392
Chest tightness.

31:53.978 --> 31:54.577
Heartache.

31:54.898 --> 31:55.537
Palpitations.

31:56.458 --> 31:57.018
Discomfort.

31:57.297 --> 31:58.537
I can't breathe.

32:01.458 --> 32:01.898
Alright.

32:02.258 --> 32:03.137
I'll go with you.

32:04.698 --> 32:05.097
Hurry up.

32:09.418 --> 32:10.178
Mr. Shen,

32:11.577 --> 32:12.938
your heart is perfectly fine.

32:13.137 --> 32:14.178
No issues whatsoever.

32:15.137 --> 32:15.698
Really?

32:16.137 --> 32:18.498
Then why do I feel chest tightness

32:18.537 --> 32:19.617
and palpitations?

32:19.938 --> 32:21.698
That's from the guilt.

32:23.218 --> 32:24.658
The possible causes

32:24.777 --> 32:25.658
could be numerous,

32:26.018 --> 32:26.577
but

32:26.738 --> 32:27.777
it's definitely not

32:27.898 --> 32:30.137
caused by cardiac issues.

32:31.218 --> 32:32.658
It's more related

32:32.898 --> 32:33.658
to work stress

32:33.898 --> 32:35.617
and emotional fluctuations.

32:37.857 --> 32:38.577
Have you

32:38.658 --> 32:40.258
been anxious

32:40.698 --> 32:42.337
about anything lately?

32:43.178 --> 32:43.777
Doctor,

32:44.577 --> 32:46.097
I don't think he's anxious

32:46.097 --> 32:46.898
about anything.

32:46.938 --> 32:48.018
But he's been

32:48.258 --> 32:49.698
tired and exhausted

32:49.872 --> 32:51.888
since he's been flying to
many countries every day.

32:52.418 --> 32:53.498
I mean, walking to...

32:53.537 --> 32:54.018
Right?

32:54.458 --> 32:56.097
Walking to many countries every day.

32:56.498 --> 32:57.057
So tiring.

32:58.978 --> 32:59.698
Mr. Shen,

33:00.218 --> 33:02.018
you must rest
despite your heavy schedule.

33:02.337 --> 33:03.617
I'll prescribe some nourishing

33:03.658 --> 33:04.537
and calming

33:04.698 --> 33:05.458
medications.

33:05.537 --> 33:06.057
Listen.

33:06.377 --> 33:07.537
Since we can't

33:07.577 --> 33:08.498
find the cause here,

33:08.817 --> 33:10.337
maybe I should get

33:10.698 --> 33:12.218
a comprehensive checkup.

33:14.057 --> 33:15.218
That's a good idea.

33:16.458 --> 33:17.658
We can rule out

33:17.658 --> 33:18.498
other possibilities.

33:18.817 --> 33:19.898
You and your wife

33:20.418 --> 33:21.537
will be more reassured.

33:21.898 --> 33:22.258
Okay.

33:23.137 --> 33:23.617
I will

33:23.817 --> 33:25.498
schedule you for an MRI first.

33:26.097 --> 33:26.617
No,

33:27.018 --> 33:28.057
I think I need

33:28.658 --> 33:30.097
comprehensive tests,

33:30.777 --> 33:32.617
beginning with ENT

33:33.698 --> 33:34.898
and ophthalmology.

33:35.938 --> 33:36.458
Alright.

33:48.097 --> 33:48.817
Hello, doctor.

33:56.570 --> 33:58.923
(Medical Examination Center)

34:01.626 --> 34:03.984
(ENT Department)

34:06.864 --> 34:08.784
(Ophthalmology Department)

34:13.530 --> 34:16.112
(Ophthalmology Department)

34:17.306 --> 34:20.816
(Colonoscopy Room)

34:21.498 --> 34:22.137
Doctor.

34:22.330 --> 34:23.440
(Colonoscopy Room,
Respiratory Endoscopy Room)

34:23.440 --> 34:24.368
(Gastroenterology Department)

34:43.546 --> 34:46.096
(Colonoscopy Room)

34:46.096 --> 34:49.136
(Respiratory Endoscopy Room)

34:49.136 --> 34:50.544
(Gastroenterology Department)

34:53.242 --> 34:55.632
(Urology Department)

35:01.754 --> 35:13.537
(Men's Restroom)

35:13.537 --> 35:14.617
Are you done?

35:17.257 --> 35:18.137
Stop rushing me.

35:18.217 --> 35:18.858
Almost done.

35:20.137 --> 35:21.737
Can you hurry up?

35:22.057 --> 35:22.898
They'll close soon.

35:22.898 --> 35:24.737
(Men's Restroom)

35:24.737 --> 35:26.097
What's the rush?

35:27.137 --> 35:28.097
These matters

35:28.778 --> 35:30.137
can't be rushed.

35:30.818 --> 35:32.097
I'm waiting for the urge.

35:32.097 --> 35:32.657
You've been

35:33.298 --> 35:34.177
waiting for the urge

35:34.177 --> 35:35.097
for over half an hour.

35:35.697 --> 35:36.858
It's 4:55 PM now.

35:36.898 --> 35:37.898
They close at 5:30 PM.

35:37.938 --> 35:39.057
We'll be late.

35:40.978 --> 35:41.737
Now I feel it.

35:42.818 --> 35:43.537
Now?

35:43.778 --> 35:44.257
Hold it in.

35:45.257 --> 35:46.257
Pee after the divorce.

35:48.090 --> 35:50.338
(Service Suspended)

35:50.338 --> 35:50.778
Hurry.

35:51.177 --> 35:51.818
Excuse me.

35:52.137 --> 35:52.737
Sorry.

35:53.057 --> 35:53.537
Uh.

35:54.057 --> 35:54.657
Hurry.

35:55.137 --> 35:56.097
(Civil Affairs Bureau)
We're getting a divorce.

35:56.577 --> 35:57.657
Check the time.

35:57.697 --> 35:58.657
It's 5:35 PM.

35:58.818 --> 35:59.898
The system's shut down.

35:59.938 --> 36:00.778
Come back tomorrow.

36:04.057 --> 36:05.057
We're really sorry.

36:05.177 --> 36:06.818
Can you make an exception

36:06.978 --> 36:07.898
and do it for us?

36:08.458 --> 36:10.257
Did you complete the cooling-off period?

36:10.577 --> 36:11.137
Yes.

36:13.257 --> 36:14.217
It's been thirty days.

36:16.378 --> 36:17.458
So are you still getting

36:17.577 --> 36:18.338
divorced?

36:19.177 --> 36:19.697
Yes.

36:21.378 --> 36:21.778
Okay.

36:22.018 --> 36:23.338
Submit the application

36:23.378 --> 36:24.177
again today.

36:24.537 --> 36:25.697
Come back on the 8th

36:26.018 --> 36:27.458
next month before 5:30 PM.

36:32.737 --> 36:33.177
Wait.

36:33.978 --> 36:35.898
Another cooling-off period?

36:36.217 --> 36:37.617
You missed the deadline.

36:37.818 --> 36:39.338
Your previous divorce application

36:39.378 --> 36:40.818
was automatically voided.

36:40.898 --> 36:42.298
You'll have to redo it.

36:42.697 --> 36:43.378
Remember.

36:43.418 --> 36:44.458
Be punctual next time.

36:44.537 --> 36:45.338
Otherwise,

36:45.338 --> 36:46.577
you'll come a third time.

36:56.498 --> 36:57.458
Glaring won't help.

36:58.097 --> 36:59.338
I didn't make the rules.

37:14.298 --> 37:16.217
8th next month.
First thing in the morning.

37:26.097 --> 37:26.697
Ma'am.

37:27.177 --> 37:28.097
You can clock out now.

37:29.177 --> 37:29.617
Thank you.

37:40.538 --> 37:43.057
(Audio & Film Equipment Museum)

37:43.057 --> 37:44.657
You talk business here, Mr. Liang?

37:45.458 --> 37:46.458
My work style

37:46.458 --> 37:47.177
is unique.

37:47.378 --> 37:48.577
My business partners should

37:48.577 --> 37:49.458
get used to it.

37:51.617 --> 37:52.177
Let's go.

37:57.658 --> 38:00.624
(Audio & Film Equipment Museum)

38:02.778 --> 38:04.378
This is a private museum

38:05.018 --> 38:05.778
run by my friend.

38:07.577 --> 38:08.778
I'm their

38:09.057 --> 38:10.418
VVVVIP guest.

38:11.818 --> 38:13.378
Whenever I need some time alone,

38:13.378 --> 38:14.378
this is where I come.

38:15.097 --> 38:16.338
It's open for me 24/7.

38:16.898 --> 38:17.697
No disturbances.

38:21.537 --> 38:22.217
I can tell

38:22.217 --> 38:23.458
you love films.

38:29.418 --> 38:30.338
When I was young,

38:31.057 --> 38:32.137
my dad was busy working.

38:33.338 --> 38:34.418
My sister studied abroad.

38:36.537 --> 38:37.697
Only my mom was there

38:38.657 --> 38:39.697
during my childhood.

38:42.378 --> 38:43.378
She loved movies.

38:44.097 --> 38:45.338
She took me to a movie

38:45.338 --> 38:46.177
almost every day.

38:47.898 --> 38:49.577
Those two magical hours

38:51.617 --> 38:52.338
were her gift

38:52.338 --> 38:53.257
of happiness.

38:57.778 --> 38:59.137
I wanted to study filming

39:03.378 --> 39:04.257
in college.

39:05.577 --> 39:06.498
But I had to

39:06.657 --> 39:07.697
study finance as my dad

39:07.697 --> 39:08.298
requested.

39:11.577 --> 39:12.418
Then

39:14.697 --> 39:15.537
my parents passed.

39:16.617 --> 39:17.657
My sister was busy.

39:20.217 --> 39:21.338
I went to the movies alone.

39:27.257 --> 39:28.458
So this is a collection

39:28.458 --> 39:29.617
of your regrets.

39:35.057 --> 39:35.938
As a director,

39:36.498 --> 39:37.938
I missed my leading lady.

39:39.298 --> 39:40.217
But as a businessman,

39:41.737 --> 39:42.418
I found you.

39:43.858 --> 39:45.498
My one-in-a-lifetime

39:47.577 --> 39:48.137
partner.

39:48.978 --> 39:50.338
I didn't have the privilege

39:50.737 --> 39:52.458
to watch movies as a kid.

39:54.298 --> 39:55.737
But I loved TV shows

39:57.257 --> 39:58.657
and news anchors.

40:00.137 --> 40:01.298
So I wondered

40:02.778 --> 40:03.858
whether I could

40:05.338 --> 40:06.458
become like them.

40:08.177 --> 40:08.697
See,

40:09.458 --> 40:10.217
we have a lot

40:10.257 --> 40:11.018
in common.

40:11.978 --> 40:12.498
Right?

40:18.737 --> 40:19.858
This...

40:21.057 --> 40:22.057
looks like...

40:22.298 --> 40:24.057
The same as the one in Roman Holiday.

40:24.298 --> 40:24.978
Exactly.

40:25.298 --> 40:26.418
I've watched that movie.

40:32.217 --> 40:33.057
Can I take a photo?

40:33.537 --> 40:34.097
Let me do it.

40:34.298 --> 40:35.097
Thanks, I got this.

40:58.778 --> 41:00.097
I don't like the ending.

41:01.498 --> 41:02.617
One day to love.

41:03.137 --> 41:04.298
A lifetime to forget.

41:05.018 --> 41:05.498
How tragic.

41:06.057 --> 41:07.018
What a tragedy.

41:09.177 --> 41:10.938
All the kids would think

41:10.938 --> 41:12.057
that a princess

41:12.418 --> 41:13.978
should break through all obstacles

41:14.057 --> 41:15.537
and be with her true love.

41:16.737 --> 41:17.257
Only adults

41:17.257 --> 41:18.537
realize that people

41:19.617 --> 41:21.018
from different backgrounds

41:21.137 --> 41:22.657
have different responsibilities

41:22.818 --> 41:23.537
and problems.

41:24.858 --> 41:25.537
A loving couple

41:25.537 --> 41:26.858
may not end up together.

41:28.378 --> 41:29.378
Roman Holiday

41:31.338 --> 41:32.458
wasn't really a fairy tale.

41:34.378 --> 41:35.217
I remember

41:35.257 --> 41:36.137
there was a line.

41:39.577 --> 41:40.816
"Lift up your head, princess.

41:41.298 --> 41:42.577
If not, the crown falls."

41:44.217 --> 41:45.378
I share this line with you.

41:46.697 --> 41:47.298
But I prefer

41:47.298 --> 41:48.498
another line.

41:50.617 --> 41:51.818
"Life isn't always

41:51.818 --> 41:53.057
what one likes."

42:19.217 --> 42:19.737
Hey, pretty.

42:20.697 --> 42:21.537
Want to be the first

42:21.537 --> 42:22.458
to ride shotgun?

42:23.458 --> 42:23.978
Hop on.

42:25.697 --> 42:26.378
Mr. Liang.

42:31.697 --> 42:33.057
Meiru. What a coincidence.

42:34.257 --> 42:35.338
She is...?

42:37.137 --> 42:37.537
Hello.

42:39.137 --> 42:39.978
I'm Xu Yan,

42:40.657 --> 42:41.840
Mr. Liang's business partner.

42:43.577 --> 42:44.298
This is...

42:44.338 --> 42:45.097
I'm Meiru.

42:45.498 --> 42:46.577
I work in self-media.

42:51.617 --> 42:52.217
Mr. Liang,

42:52.657 --> 42:54.137
you tricked me into hopping on,

42:54.177 --> 42:54.737
but this bike

42:54.737 --> 42:55.778
couldn't even start.

42:56.298 --> 42:57.537
Why are you riding it again?

43:02.858 --> 43:04.057
I guess I'm not

43:04.057 --> 43:05.018
your first passenger.

43:09.057 --> 43:09.938
Give me a second.

43:12.378 --> 43:13.137
Come here.

43:13.217 --> 43:13.617
Come on.

43:13.818 --> 43:14.537
Come on.

43:16.577 --> 43:17.257
Why are you here?

43:17.737 --> 43:18.418
You lectured me

43:18.458 --> 43:19.577
on film history.

43:19.778 --> 43:20.938
It was really enlightening.

43:21.338 --> 43:22.458
So I'm planning

43:22.458 --> 43:23.537
a movie salon event.

43:23.898 --> 43:24.938
Will you tell me more?

43:27.018 --> 43:28.097
Did you sign up for

43:28.097 --> 43:29.217
that art program

43:29.338 --> 43:29.978
I suggested?

43:32.018 --> 43:32.498
You didn't.

43:33.458 --> 43:34.657
That program

43:34.697 --> 43:36.137
will do you good.

43:36.657 --> 43:37.657
Complete the course,

43:37.778 --> 43:39.097
and we'll discuss art.

43:39.257 --> 43:39.737
Alright?

43:42.298 --> 43:43.498
Remember to call me then.

43:45.057 --> 43:45.537
Go ahead.

43:49.898 --> 43:50.617
There you are.

43:53.858 --> 43:54.737
Don't get me wrong.

43:54.737 --> 43:55.697
She was just

43:55.697 --> 43:56.617
an art enthusiast.

43:57.097 --> 43:58.177
I get it, Mr. Liang.

43:59.177 --> 44:00.617
You're just helping girls

44:00.657 --> 44:01.978
improve themselves

44:02.057 --> 44:03.217
as their mentor.

44:03.697 --> 44:04.418
Right?

44:05.737 --> 44:06.938
I genuinely want to

44:07.217 --> 44:08.657
show care and support

44:09.057 --> 44:10.537
to the girls I meet.

44:12.498 --> 44:13.418
Well done.

44:14.177 --> 44:15.298
I have many other

44:15.338 --> 44:16.057
good qualities.

44:16.057 --> 44:17.298
You should get to know me.

44:17.418 --> 44:18.338
Like our outfits.

44:18.617 --> 44:20.257
Don't you see our outfits
match perfectly?

44:20.657 --> 44:22.137
Aren't we in sync?

44:28.602 --> 44:30.800
(Xu Yan)

44:50.498 --> 44:51.338
Haoming.

44:52.298 --> 44:52.938
What a surprise.

44:58.778 --> 44:59.818
You know what?

45:00.657 --> 45:01.697
Rumors have been

45:02.137 --> 45:03.657
spreading in our circle.

45:05.097 --> 45:05.978
Xu Yan

45:06.418 --> 45:07.378
and Jiang Liang

45:07.898 --> 45:09.177
are really hitting it off.

45:11.858 --> 45:12.498
You're drunk.

45:20.217 --> 45:21.818
Don't you know Jiang Liang?

45:23.137 --> 45:24.858
He's a ladies' man

45:25.338 --> 45:26.818
who never commits to anyone.

45:27.617 --> 45:29.137
Even he fell for Xu Yan

45:29.137 --> 45:30.577
and got completely infatuated.

45:32.057 --> 45:33.938
Xu Yan is quite something.

45:37.898 --> 45:39.097
Or perhaps

45:40.498 --> 45:42.298
she's desperate to find her next target.

45:45.298 --> 45:46.537
Xu Yan is my wife.

45:47.257 --> 45:48.097
Watch your mouth.

45:49.338 --> 45:50.378
Still defending her.

45:51.338 --> 45:52.298
She's just using you

45:52.298 --> 45:53.137
as a rich fool.

45:53.137 --> 45:54.137
And you still defend her.

45:54.898 --> 45:55.537
Shen Haoming.

45:55.737 --> 45:57.018
You should really check

45:57.137 --> 45:57.737
whether she's

45:57.737 --> 45:58.657
cheated on you.

45:58.898 --> 45:59.617
Or maybe

45:59.617 --> 46:00.537
you're used to it.

46:06.057 --> 46:07.617
I'm the only one loyal to you.

46:10.018 --> 46:11.057
But you won't even

46:11.097 --> 46:12.018
look my way, will you?

46:18.978 --> 46:20.057
You're such a coward.

46:31.378 --> 46:32.577
You're finally looking at me.

46:33.778 --> 46:34.617
Hit me then.

46:34.778 --> 46:35.697
Why don't you hit me?

46:35.737 --> 46:36.418
Go ahead.

